name: Winded Skies
description: An Unique and Exclusive Big Cartel selling Digital Image, to be used as you like. When you’ve purchased the image you’ll receive an 1212x1243px (16x17in) + frame jpg file in an email within 24 hours. PayPal provides an easy and secure checkout for your purchase. You don't need to have an account or sign up for one. But if you don't have a Bank Card, you can pay by Money Transfer. Please contact me to arrange payment at madebydesigner@gmail.com You can ask for a customized change on color and graphics. And if you're looking to commission Graphic Design please contact me to let me know what you're after.
